text:
This is just another way of compromised organisations like the MCB channelling acts of worship into support for their political friends. 

Fear Allh and stop using Islm as emotional fuel for projects that fundamentally oppose Islm. 

@MuslimCouncil

"Ibn Taymiyyah   said;

Non-Mahrams can't be trusted even if they were the most fearing of Allah.

For indeed, hearts change rapidly and the Shaytan is on the lookout, verily the Prophet  said;

A man is not alone with a woman except that the third of them is the Shaytan"
